title: IGtolFrame.DeleteIndicator
description: Deletes the tolerance indicator at the specified Gtol frame indicator index.

parameters.name: IndicatorIndex
parameters.description: One-based index of tolerance indicator to delete from the frame

returns: True if tolerance indicator successfully deleted, false if not
remarks:
Before calling this method, use
IGtolFrame:GetIndicatorCount
to determine IndicatorIndex.
